data.description: Discover the charm & potential of this delightful Bellevue Ranch home today. Upon entry you will be greeted by the warmth of original hardwood floors that extend throughout the living room, dining room, & all three bedrooms. The living room, with its hardwood flooring, bathes in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance that's hard to resist & is perfect for both quiet evenings & lively gatherings. The kitchen offers ample cabinet space for all your storage needs & appliances that are included.The main floor full bathroom is strategically located near all three bedrooms featuring an updated single solid surface vanity.The lower level features a 3/4 bath & a large blank canvas space ready for you to customize & finish according to your preferences, the opportunities are endless. Have peace of mind with this home being pre-inspected, a newer AC unit, updates made to the furnace, & the inclusion of all appliances. Make it yours today & don't miss out on this unparalleled opportunity.
